<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<graphml xmlns="http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns http://graphml.graphdrawing.org/xmlns/1.0/graphml.xsd">
  <key id="d6" for="edge" attr.name="order" attr.type="long" />
  <key id="d5" for="edge" attr.name="source_id" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d4" for="edge" attr.name="description" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d3" for="edge" attr.name="weight" attr.type="double" />
  <key id="d2" for="node" attr.name="source_id" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d1" for="node" attr.name="description" attr.type="string" />
  <key id="d0" for="node" attr.name="entity_type" attr.type="string" />
  <graph edgedefault="undirected">
    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_14&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image is a simple, monochromatic icon featuring a stylized gas pump or fuel dispenser. The icon is rendered in shades of white and light gray against a solid black background. The main body of the pump is a vertical rectangle, with a smaller rectangular base at the bottom. Extending from the upper right side of the pump's body is a handle or nozzle, depicted with a slight curve and a distinct shape. Above the nozzle, at the top right corner of the pump, there is a small, rectangular shape resembling a sheet of paper or a flag, commonly associated with a receipt or a sign at a gas station. The overall design is clean and minimalist, clearly representing a fuel station or gasoline service."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_14.jpg</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FUEL PUMP ICON&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A black and white icon depicting a stylized fuel pump. It features a rectangular pump body with a dispensing nozzle and hose extending to the right, typically used to symbolize a gas station, fuel, or refueling."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_14.jpg</data>
    </node>
    <edge source="&quot;IMAGE_14&quot;" target="&quot;FUEL PUMP ICON&quot;">
      <data key="d3">10.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Fuel Pump Icon是从image_14中提取的实体。"</data>
      <data key="d5">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_14.jpg</data>
      <data key="d6">1</data>
    </edge>
  </graph>
</graphml>
